Key Match Events: Rayan Raveloson scored for Madagascar in the 25th minute.
Couturier scored for Madagascar in the 45+2 minute.
Manneh scored for Gambia in the 85th minute.
Minteh scored for Gambia in the 90+7 minute.
Pre-Game Insights: Madagascar and Gambia will be looking to secure their first win in Group A of the 2025 Africa Cup of Nations qualifiers.
Romuald Rakotondrabe's men have failed to win any of their last 12 AFCON qualifying matches since November 2019.
Gambia were denied their first win in their race for a place in Morocco as they fell to a 2-1 defeat against Tunisia.
